summary: Adds a chest with executioner equipment in Castle Dour.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a chest with a playable set of executioner equipment to Castle Dour.

The armour was previously unavailable to characters, but now, it\'s yours to use! I\'ve made it so that it can be used by both male and female characters using the same model (previously, it would appear as Dark Brotherhood robes on female characters), but female characters wearing it will look a bit mannish.

Done by request for Daventry.
author: Captain Lhurgoyf
